gedit-plugins: gedit-plugins (GNOME Text Editor Plugins)
gedit-plugins:
gedit-plugins: gEdit is a small but powerful text editor designed for GNOME.  It
gedit-plugins: includes such features as split-screen mode, a plugin API, which
gedit-plugins: allows gEdit to be extended to support many features while remaining
gedit-plugins: small at its core, multiple document editing through the use of a
gedit-plugins: 'tabbed' notebook and many more functions, including Python
gedit-plugins: modules.
gedit-plugins:
gedit-plugins: This package contains additional plugins for gEdit.
